], except where noted. The two bonus tracks are available with electronic versions of the album, but not on the CD. An extended version of '''''Barton Hollow''''' was released in Europe through Sony Music on March 1, 2012, which contained the 12 tracks included with the North American release, the 2 bonus tracks from the electronic version, plus 4 additional tracks.\n\n{{track listing\n| collapsed = \n| headline = \n| title1 = 20 Years\n| length1 = 3:02\n| title2 = I've Got This Friend\n| length2 = 3:24\n| title3 = C'est la mort\n| length3 = 2:30\n| title4 = To Whom It May Concern\n| length4 = 3:32\n| title5 = Poison & Wine\n| writer5 = Williams, White, [[Chris Lindsey]]\n| length5 = 3:40\n| title6 = My Father's Father\n| length6 = 3:21\n| title7 = [[Barton Hollow (song)|Barton Hollow]]\n| length7 = 3:26\n| title8 = The Violet Hour\n| length8 = 3:26\n| title9 = Girl With the Red Balloon\n| length9 = 3:50\n| title10 = Falling\n| length10 = 3:59\n| title11 = Forget Me Not\n| length11 = 2:57\n| title12 = Birds of a Feather\n| length12 = 3:06\n}}\n\n{{track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Electronic version bonus tracks\n| title13 = [[I Want You Back]] \n| writer13 = [[Berry Gordy]], [[Freddie Perren]], [[Alphonzo Mizell]] and [[Deke Richards]]\n| length13 = 3:15\n| title14 = [[Dance Me to the End of Love]]\n| writer14 = [[Leonard Cohen]]\n| length14 = 3:05\n}}\n\n{{track listing\n| collapsed =  yes\n| headline = European edition bonus tracks\n| title13 = [[Billie Jean]]\n| writer13 = Michael Jackson\n| length13 = 4:09\n| title14 = [[I Want You Back]] \n| writer14 = [[Berry Gordy]], [[Freddie Perren]], [[Alphonzo Mizell]] and [[Deke Richards]]\n| length14 = 3:15\n| title15 = [[Dance Me to the End of Love]]\n| writer15 = Leonard Cohen\n| length15 = 3:05\n| title16 = [[You Are My Sunshine]]\n| writer16 = Jimmie Davis and [[Charles Mitchell (songwriter)|Charles Mitchell]]\n| length16 = 3:09\n| title17 = Goodbye Girl\n| writer17 = John Paul White; Joy Williams\n| length17 = 4:00\n| title18 = Marionette\n| note18 = Demo) (Bonus\n| writer18 = John Paul White; Joy Williams\n| length18 = 3:01\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\nListed in AllMusic.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/barton-hollow-mw0002103142/credits |title=Barton Hollow - The Civil Wars &#124; Credits |publisher=AllMusic |date=February 1, 2011 |accessdate=August 24, 2013}}</ref>\n\n* [[Joy Williams (singer)|Joy Williams]]: lead vocals, background vocals, piano, [[Hohner]] organ, [[bell (instrument)|bell]]s\n* [[John Paul White]]: lead vocals, background vocals, acoustic guitar, electric guitar, [[resonator guitar]], banjo, bass guitar\n* Andy Leftwich: fiddle, [[mandolin]]\n* David Davidson: violin\n* John Catchings: cello\n* Jerry McPherson: electric guitar\n* [[J.T. Corenflos]]: electric guitar\n* [[Dan Dugmore]]: [[pedal steel guitar]]\n* Tim Lauer: keyboards, synthesizer, [[keyboard bass]], organ, \"tiny keyboard\"\n* [[Charlie Peacock]]: electric piano, trumpet, producer, additional engineering\n* [[Barry Bales]]: double bass\n* Ken Lewis: percussion\n* Richie Biggs: engineer, mixer\n* Richard Dodd: mastering\n\n==Charts==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Chart (2011\u201312)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Belgian Albums Chart]] (Wallonia)<ref name=bdch>{{cite web|author=Steffen Hung |url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Civil+Wars&titel=Barton+Hollow&cat=a |title=The Civil Wars - Barton Hollow |publisher=dutchcharts.nl |date=March 17, 2012 |accessdate=March 26, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104063022/http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Civil+Wars&titel=Barton+Hollow&cat=a |archivedate=November 4, 2014  }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 37\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=the civil wars|chart=Canadian Albums}}|title=The Civil Wars Album & Song Chart History \u2013 Canadian Albums|work=[[Billboa